{
  "title": "Music Streaming — System Overview",
  "uid": "music-streaming-overview",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["music-streaming", "overview"],
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Total Request Rate (all services)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{uri!~\".*actuator.*\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "total req/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "single"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "HTTP Error Rate by Service",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{uri!~\".*actuator.*\",status=~\"5..\"}[1m])) by (job)",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "p99 Latency by Service",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{uri!~\".*actuator.*\"}[1m])) by (le, job))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}} p99",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {"tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 2}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Service Health",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "up{job=~\"auth-service|catalog-service|streaming-service|playlist-service|search-service|analytics-service|recommendation-service|notification-service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}, "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}}}
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "green", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Kafka Consumer Lag (all groups)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 16, "w": 6, "h": 6},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumergroup_lag)",
          "legendFormat": "total lag",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1000},
              {"color": "red", "value": 10000}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "JVM Heap Usage by Service",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {"x": 6, "y": 16, "w": 18, "h": 6},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "sum(jvm_memory_used_bytes{area=\"heap\"}) by (job) / sum(jvm_memory_max_bytes{area=\"heap\"}) by (job)",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.7},
              {"color": "red", "value": 0.9}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Top 10 Songs by Play Count",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 22, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Top 10 Songs — Not Yet Available\n\nThis panel requires `analytics-service` to emit a `playback_event_total{song_id}` Micrometer counter.\n\n**To enable:** add a `Counter.builder(\"playback_event_total\").tag(\"song_id\", songId).register(meterRegistry).increment()` call in `analytics-service`'s `AnalyticsService.recordBatch()` method, then replace this panel with:\n\n```\ntopk(10, sum(increase(playback_event_total[24h])) by (song_id))\n```\n\n*(S-03 partial compliance — traffic, latency, error rate, and service health panels are fully operational)*"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Load Generator Active VUs",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 22, "w": 12, "h": 6},
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "expr": "k6_vus",
          "legendFormat": "active VUs",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": ""},
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "noValue": "0 (load generator idle)"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "blue", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 100},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1000}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    }
  ]
}
